Package de.gianfelice.aeskulab.data.container

Contains all containers, that are used to display and manage data in this application.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
EventTreeContainer Deprecated. Will be replaced in the next version
HelperContainer A simple container for all Helper objects.
LogContainer This container collects all Log objects and allows to display them inside a tree.
PlaceContainer A simple container for all Place objects.
QualificationContainer A simple container for all Qualification objects.
SquadContainer A container that holds all Squad objects and offers different methods to handle them.
SquadTypeContainer A simple container for all SquadType objects.
UnitContainer This container holds all units that can be assigned to Work objects.
UserContainer This simple container organises all User objects of this project.
VehicleContainer A container that holds all Vehicle objects and offers different methods to handle them.
WorkContainer Contains all Work objects in hierarchical order with the assigned units.
WorkItemContainer A simple container for all Work objects.
